window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sit in prison or join the military. The choice is yours. </b></p> <p>Convicted of a minor traffic violation, Rev Pelletier is conscripted into the Perseus Union Marine Corps...for up to a 30-year term of service.&nbsp;</p> <p>Anxious to get back to his civilian life and job, Rev opts for a shorter term as a Marine Raider taking the fight to the enemy.&nbsp;</p> <p>But with extremely high mortality rates, can he and his friends survive until their term of service is over?&nbsp;</p> <p>Download <i>Sentenced to War </i>now to follow Rev through perilous battles as he fights to hold back the alien invasion. If you're a fan of <i>Old Man's War</i>, <i>Starship Troopers</i>, or <i>Armor</i>, you'll love this military-sci-fi thrill ride.</p>"; 
